FT  27 OCT 93 / UK Company News: Hawtal in the black
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A SIGNIFICANT upturn in activity enabled Hawtal Whiting, the Essex-based
automotive design engineer, to move from losses of Pounds 1.38m to profits
of Pounds 402,000 pre-tax for the half year to June 30.
