FT  27 OCT 93 / UK Company News: P&amp;O plans flotation
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
PENINSULAR and Oriental Steam Navigation yesterday announced that it was
preparing a US flotation of some 6,677 US apartments owned by Laing
Properties, a 50:50 joint venture between it and Chelsfield.
P&amp;O said it would next week file a notice with the US Securities and
Exchange Commission for the flotation of the portfolio as a real estate
investment trust.
Analysts estimate the REIT could be worth some Dollars 500m (Pounds 331m).
