<TEXT>
Suspicions that the Balladur government is cooking up a sternly
protectionist policy towards the Uruguay trade round were only confirmed at
Chatham House yesterday when Alain Lamassoure, French European Affairs
Minister, who was due to address the foreign policy think-tank on the future
