<HEADLINE>
FT  27 OCT 93 / Baby buggy
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A child-sized replica of the celebrated Bugatti Type 52 which was expected
to raise up to Pounds 1,500 for London's Great Ormond Street Hospital for
Sick Children at Brooks' automobilia auction at the London Motor Show. The
replica features a petrol engine and black leather trim
