<HEADLINE>
FT  26 OCT 93 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1993
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JOEL KIBAZO, CHRISTOPHER PRICE and CHRISTINE BUCKLEY
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
